{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1677-06_132","@resp":"mercure","head":{"value":"Lettre en chansons","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Le Nouveau Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#1":{"value":", juin 1677 (tome IV), p. 132-141","id":"/div/bibl/#1"},"note":{"@resp":"editor","#":{"value":"Il existe une autre édition parisienne, réalisée \"Suivant la Copie imprimée\" par Claude Barbin, dont la pagination diffère.","id":"/div/bibl/note/#"}},"#2":{"value":".","id":"/div/bibl/#2"}},"p":{"#1":{"value":"J’adjoûteray à ces Stances une Lettre écrite à Madame la Marquise de Louvois par Monsieur Galand, Secretaire du Cabinet. Vous la trouverez d’une nouveauté singuliere. Elle est toute en differens Couplets de Chanson sur les Airs les plus connus. Madame de Louvois estoit allée passer quelques jours à la Campagne, &amp; M","id":"/div/p/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/p/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":" Galand qui ne le cede à personne en délicatesse d’esprit, eust eu peine à luy marquer plus agreablement le chagrin qu’il avoit de son absence. La Lettre est en partie sur les grandes Actions du Roy, &amp; c’est pour cela que j’ay crû la devoir placer icy.","id":"/div/p/#2"}},"quote":{"#":[{"label":[{"#1":{"value":"LETTRE ","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label[0]/#1"},"lb":{},"#2":{"value":"EN CHANSONS,","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label[0]/#2"}},{"#":{"value":"Sur le Chant de ","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label[1]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Lancelot Turpin.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label[1]/hi/#"}}}]},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Flore dans nos Champs","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Est enfin descenduë,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les Oyseaux par leurs chants","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Annoncent sa venuë ;","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais que sert le Printemps,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quand on vous a perduë ?","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[5]/#"}}]}},{"label":{"#":{"value":"Sur le Chant de ","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/label/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Réveillez-vous Belle endormie.","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/label/hi/#"}}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Du Zephir la douce influence","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Change en vain nos Bois &amp; nos Prez,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Nous ne sentirons sa presence,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que du jour que vous reviendrez.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"label":{"value":"Sur l’Air du Traquenart.","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/label"}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Madame, que faites-vous","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De vous éloigner de nous ?","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" De ma propre main,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si je croyois mon courage,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" De ma propre main","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je me percerois le sein.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[5]/#"}}]}},{"label":{"value":"Sur l’Air de la Bordeaux.","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/label"}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A qui connoist vostre beauté charmante,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Comme nous faisons tous,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Toute saison est aimable &amp; riante","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Qui se passe avec vous.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Nul temps n’est doux","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Quand vous estes absente,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Et c’est par le mesme esprit","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Que l’heureux Coulange rit,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Et Galand lamente.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[8]/#"}}]}},{"label":{"#":{"value":"Sur le Chant de ","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/label/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"l’Echelle du Temple.","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/label/hi/#"}}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je ne hay point les Espagnols,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tant que Coulange &amp; que Bagnols.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ils ont eux-seuls tout l’avantage,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tous les plaisirs, &amp; tout l’honneur,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et ne nous laissent en partage,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que d’enrager de leur bonheur.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[5]/#"}}]}},{"label":{"#":{"value":"Sur le Chant de ","id":"/div/quote/#[10]/label/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Landeriette.","id":"/div/quote/#[10]/label/hi/#"}}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais à quoy bon tant de douleurs ?","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Nos cris, nos soûpirs &amp; nos pleurs,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Landeriette,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne vous ramenent pas icy,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Landeriette.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[4]/#"}}]}},{"label":{"#":{"value":"Sur l’Air de ","id":"/div/quote/#[12]/label/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Fichuë est toute preste.","id":"/div/quote/#[12]/label/hi/#"}}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A tous les gens de bon goust,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’ay toûjours oüy dire","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que quand l’adresse est à bout,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il faut benir Dieu de tout,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Et rire, &amp; rire, &amp; rire.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[4]/#"}}]}},{"label":{"#":{"value":"Sur le Chant de ","id":"/div/quote/#[14]/label/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"l’Année est bonne.","id":"/div/quote/#[14]/label/hi/#"}}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais venons à nostre Grand'Roy,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A luy voir tout remplir d’effroy,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il n’est bon François qui n’entonne,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  L’Année est bonne.","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"label":{"#":{"value":"Sur le Chant de ","id":"/div/quote/#[16]/label/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Puissant Roy.","id":"/div/quote/#[16]/label/hi/#"}}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il n’est pas permis de s’affliger,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"hi":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sous ses Loix ","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[1]/hi[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Loüis","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[1]/hi[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" va tout ranger.","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[1]/hi[2]/#"}}]},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Celebrons les Miracles étranges,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’ont fait pour nous son esprit &amp; son cœur,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" A l’envy prodiguons nos loüanges,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est le seul bien qui flate le Vainqueur.","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[5]/#"}}]}},{"label":{"#":{"value":"Sur l’Air ","id":"/div/quote/#[18]/label/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Beuvons à nous quatre.","id":"/div/quote/#[18]/label/hi/#"}}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Mais quoy qu’on l’adore,","